name: The Cook - ORIGINAL
description:
He is praised, he is feared, he is the most sought after individual in all of New Mexico and soon to be all of the U.S. 
The man. The myth. The legend. The creator of Blue Sky and soon to be most infamous man of all, Walter White.
The Cook.

ORIGINAL painting.

Mixed media on bristol.

Measures 11" x 14".

This painting includes two (2) random stickers while supplies last!

**If you would like this framed, add $15**

name: Let's Party - PRINT
description:
Inviting you on a psilocybin sexcapade is none other than Princess Toadstool of Super Mario Bros. fame. She is offering a 1-Up while ridin' high on our pal, Bullet Bill. The princess is the latest addition to the Video Game Visionaries series.

Printed on 110 lb. silk card-stock (the good stuff!).

Measures 11" x 17".

Each pack includes random-insert sticker(s) from BLUE731 and friends.
